## Algorithm Strategy
- Greedy matching: try longest possible real element symbols first
- Fallback to shorter real elements when needed
- Use fake elements only as last resort
- Return combination with fewest total elements
- Case insensitive matching for better user experience

## Element Styling
- Square tiles with rounded corners (border-radius: 8px)
- Subtle drop shadow for separation
- Category-based colors with vibrant flat UI palette
- Bold sans-serif fonts for symbols
- Responsive design for mobile
- Enhanced glow effects for highlighted elements
- White text for atomic numbers and masses for better contrast

## Animation Guidelines
- **Consistent Timing**: 300ms transitions across all elements
- **Purposeful Animations**: Only animate when it enhances UX
- **Smooth Easing**: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)
- **Glow Effects**: 1.5-2 second cycles for visual prominence
- **Staggered Reveals**: 100ms delays for sequential animations

## Accessibility Standards
- High contrast ratios for all color schemes
- Keyboard navigation support
- Screen reader compatibility
- Color blind support with patterns
- WCAG 2.1 AA compliance

